manga.description: In the near future, a Virtual Reality Massive Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game (VRMMORPG) called Sword Art Online has been released where players control their avatars with their bodies using a piece of technology called Nerve Gear. One day, players discover they cannot log out, as the game creator is holding them captive unless they reach the 100th floor of the game's tower and defeat the final boss. manga.title: The Ravages Of Time
alt_names: 三国志群雄伝火鳳燎原; 火鳳燎原 (Chinese); หงสาจอมราชันย์ (Thai); Hỏa Phụng Liêu Nguyên (Vietnamese - Tiếng Việt - TV); Huo Feng Liao Yuan (English); Kahou Ryougen; Sangokushi Gunyuuden Kahou Ryougen (Japanese); Sanguozhi Qunxiongzhuan: Huo Feng Liao Yuan
manga.description:
Nearly 2000 years ago, the prosperous Han dynasty of China collapsed. Heroes rose and fell, and three nations emerged--Wei, Shu, and Wu. Historians refer to this period as the Three Kingdoms period. The romance of the three kingdoms is an intriguing tale of heroic deeds, of alliance forged and broken, of loyalty and betrayal. Hong Kong artist Chan Mou retells this classic tale in "The Ravages of Time" from the perspective of the Sima clan, which in the end united the three kingdoms. Readers will be attracted by an array of well-developed characters and Chan Mou's own unique top-notch art-style.

You also may like:
+ Kingdom
+ Ruler of the Land

manga.title: Fuga: Melodies Of Steel
alt_names: 戦場のフーガ 鋼鉄のメロディ
manga.description:
The children swear revenge in the midst of war.
The official comic version of the dramatic simulation RPG “Battlefield Fuga” with the theme of “War x Revenge x Beasts” “Battlefield” 'Fuga Melody of Steel'! The manga was written by Takafumi Adachi (representative works: "DM Fighter Homura'' and "Metal Fight Beyblade,'' etc.).
＜Synopsis＞
A world made up of floating islands of various sizes - a floating continent, where two types of races, "inuhito" and "nekohito" live.
Marto, an Inuhito boy, lives peacefully with his younger sister Mei while herding sheep in the remote village of Petit Mona. One day, the village is suddenly attacked by the northeastern country ``Berman Empire,'' and it burns to the ground overnight. How could something like this happen... Marto and the others were confused, and a mysterious voice came from the radio...! ?
Children caught up in the war board the mysterious giant tank ``Taranis'' to retrieve their abducted families!
As an appendix exclusive to the book, it also includes setting drawings by Takafumi Adachi and a development blog by Hiroshi Matsuyama, general director of the game software ``Fuga of Battlefield'' and CEO of Cyber ​​Connect Two Co., Ltd.

Mei Inukai, a receptionist at an IT company, is a huge dog lover. One night, during a full moon, she discovers a weakened wolf and can't resist taking it in. But when she wakes up the next morning, she finds an unfamiliar werewolf in her bed who both attacks and kisses her!
